=== EXAMPLE: scdoc_Classes_BPZ2_ex2 ===

DESCRIPTION: A very_bright mixed sound, with saw_like oscillator character around 51 Hz, featuring punchy attack and dynamic envelope, with chaotic spectral movement, filtered with resonant_highpass character, and spectrally dense.

CATEGORIES:
  attack_time: punchy
  brightness: very_bright
  crest_factor_db: dynamic
  envelope_flatness: flat
  harmonic_to_noise_ratio: mixed
  spectral_complexity_mean: dense
  spectral_flux_normalized: chaotic
  spectral_slope: highpass
  temporal_centroid: balanced

SYNTHESIS CONCEPTS (key values):
[oscillator]
  fundamental_freq: 51.4651
  harmonic_decay_rate: 3.6599
  harmonic_regularity: 0.9141
  pitch_clarity: 4.0668
  inharmonicity: 0.0303
  type: saw_like
[filter]
  spectral_slope: 6.1338
  resonance_freq: 10249.8047

